                    text: "CRABS AND SKELETONS ARE THE LEAST OF IT. THE DARK KNIGHTS RIDE THESE HEIGHTS."),
                Say(speaker: Some("ROLAND"), portrait: Some("swordsman"),
                    text: "THEN WE CLIMB - AND WE DO NOT STOP UNTIL WE REACH THE SUMMIT."),
            ],
        ),
        CutsceneDef(
            id: "gareth_joins",
            steps: [
                Say(speaker: Some("???"), portrait: Some("hermit"),
                    text: "STILL BREATHING, AFTER ALL THAT? NO ONE CLEARS THIS PASS. NO ONE."),
                Say(speaker: Some("ROLAND"), portrait: Some("swordsman"),
                    text: "WHO ARE YOU? YOU MOVE LIKE NO HERMIT I EVER MET."),
                Say(speaker: Some("GARETH"), portrait: Some("hermit"),
